  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Girls&apos; Education Forum</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Forum will bring together leading policy makers, key stakeholders and leading advocates for girls&#x2019; education from across the international community.  It will showcase the strong evidence base of what works in tackling the barriers to girls&#x2019; education in order to inform new policy and financial commitments to achieve Global Goal 4.  In addition, it will raise public awareness of the issues and will set out how the international community will respond to the challenges, to encourage a continued momentum that the public can get behind through to UNGA and beyond.</narrative>
  </description>
